icus  Phoenix 40  1986  Devine  A M   A Pawn Sacrifice at the Battle of the Granicus  Ancient World 18  1 2  Fall  1988  3 20 E  Badian   The Battle of the Granicus  A New Look  Ancient Macedonia 2  Institute for Balkan Studies 155  Thessaloniki 1977 271 293  Nikolitsis  N  T   The Battle of Granicus  Skrifter Utgivna av Svenska Institute i Athen XXI n  4  1974  Issus Barker  Philip  Alexander the Great s Campaigns  Cambridge  1979  Devine  A M   The Location of the Battle of Issus  LCM 5 1980  3 10  Devine  A M   The Strategies of Alexander the Great and Darius III in the Battle of Issus campaign  Ancient World 12 1985  25 38  Devine A M   Grand Tactics at the Battle of Issus  Ancient World 12  1985  39 59  Glover  R F   The Tactical Handling of the Elephant  G R 17  1948  1 11  Glover R   The Elephant in Ancient Warfare  CJ 39  1943 44  257 269  Janke  A   Die Schlacht bei Issus  Klio 10  1910  137 177  Gaugamela cf  Markov Barker  Philip  Alexander the Great s Campaigns  Cambridge  1979  Devine  A M   The Battle of Gaugamela  A Tactical and Source Critical Study  Ancient World 13  1986  87 116  Fuller  J F  C  The Generalship of Alexander the Great   1960  pp  167 74  Griffith G T   Alexander s Generalship at Gaugamela  JHS 67  1947  77 89  Marsden  E W  The Campaign of Gaugamela  Liverpool  1964  Indian Campaign Eggermont  Alexander s Campaigns in Sind and Baluchistan and the Siege of the Brahmin Town of Harmatelia  Louvain  1975  Devine  A M   The Battle of Hydaspes  A Tactical and Source Critical Study  AncW 14  1987  Ipsus B  Bar Kockva  The Seleucid Army  Organization and Tactics in the Great Campaigns Cambridge  1976  Paraitacene Devine  A M   Diodorus  Account of the Battle of Paraitacene  317 B C  Ancient World 12  1985  75 86  Gabiene Devine  A M   Diodorus  Account of the Battle of Gabiene  Ancient World 12  1985  87 96  Hellenistic Age   General Austin  M M   Hellenistic kings  war  and the economy  CQ 36  1986  450 466  Gabbert  J J   Piracy in the ea